The design features 8 photo squares where you can place your own pictures (grandkids, pets, memorable family events, etc) surrounding a center square with editable text. The example reads "Best Grandma Ever" but the text is fully editable – just use the easy provided templates to complete your own custom message. The example photos shown are also easy to replace with your own photographs – square shots (like Instagram) work best. The center square color can be changed to whatever color you want – just customize by changing the background color within the design tools.
